      </div>
      <div class="wif-card">
        <div class="wif-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Businesses About to Invest in a New Website</h3>
        <p>Before spending ₹30,000–₹2,00,000 on a redesign, find out what's actually broken. You may need fewer changes than you think, or more fundamental ones.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="wif-card">
        <div class="wif-icon">📈</div>
        <h3>Established Businesses Ready to Scale Their Online Presence</h3>
        <p>You have an established customer base offline, but your website doesn't reflect your reputation. The audit identifies exactly what's stopping your digital presence from matching your real-world standing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 7: WHY FREE
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="why-free reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-free-inner">
      <div class="why-free-content">
        <span class="section-label">Transparency</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Why Is This Audit Free?</h2>
        <p>Most businesses ask this, and it's a fair question. Here is our honest answer.</p>
        <p>We offer free audits because the best way to demonstrate our expertise is to show you what we find, not just tell you what we can do. A detailed, honest audit report earns more trust in 48 hours than any sales pitch ever could.</p>
        <p>Some businesses who receive the audit fix the issues themselves, with their current team or another agency. That is completely fine. We would rather help your business improve than hide our knowledge behind a paywall.</p>
        <p>Others reach out to us to fix the issues we found. Those conversations start from a position of complete trust, because we've already proven we know what we're doing. That's how we build long-term client relationships.</p>
        <p>No hidden trial periods. No data harvesting. No follow-up cold calls if you don't want them. Just a useful report.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-free-callout">
        <div class="why-free-callout-inner">
          <div class="why-free-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
          <ul class="why-free-list">
            <li>Honest findings, good or bad</li>
            <li>No upselling inside the report</li>
            <li>No cold calls unless you ask for them</li>
            <li>No sharing your website data with anyone</li>
            <li>Delivered within 48 hours, guaranteed</li>
            <li>Written in plain language, not technical jargon</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#audit-form" class="btn btn-primary">Get My Free Audit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 8: COMMON ISSUES WE FIND
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="common-issues reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">What We Typically Find</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The 6 Most Common Issues in Ahmedabad Business Websites</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="issues-grid">
      <div class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-num">01</div>
        <h3>No Google Business Profile (or an unclaimed one)</h3>
        <p>Over 60% of local business websites we audit are either not connected to a GBP at all, or have a GBP with incorrect information. This is the single fastest fix with the biggest local SEO impact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-num">02</div>
        <h3>Failing mobile performance (below 50 PageSpeed score)</h3>
        <p>Templates and WordPress sites loaded with plugins routinely score 30–50 on mobile. With 75%+ of Gujarat's internet traffic on phones, this is an invisible lead killer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-num">03</div>
        <h3>Missing or weak call-to-action</h3>
        <p>Most business websites say what they do but never explicitly tell the visitor what to do next. No "Call Now", no "Book a Consultation", no "Get a Quote", just text and a footer phone number.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-num">04</div>
        <h3>Generic title tags (same title on every page)</h3>
        <p>"Home, XYZ Company" as the title tag on every single page. This means Google has no signal to rank your individual pages for specific keywords. Simple to fix, significant impact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-num">05</div>
        <h3>No trust signals above the fold</h3>
        <p>Visitors decide in 5 seconds whether to trust your site. Most business websites bury their experience, testimonials, and credentials at the bottom of the page, if they have them at all.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="issue-card">
        <div class="issue-num">06</div>
        <h3>Missing or broken Google Analytics setup</h3>
        <p>Over 70% of websites we audit have either no analytics, a misconfigured setup, or duplicate tracking that inflates numbers. Without accurate data, there's no way to improve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
