<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 10: FAQ
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="audit-faq reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Questions</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">About the Free Audit</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="audit-faq-grid">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is this really free? What's the catch?</summary>
        <p>It's completely free. No catch, no credit card, no obligation to hire us. We offer free audits because it builds trust, businesses that receive an honest, useful audit are more likely to work with us later. But many businesses just use the report and that's fine too.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How long does the audit take?</summary>
        <p>You'll receive your audit report within 48 business hours of submitting the form. For most websites, it's done within 24 hours.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do I need to give you access to my website?</summary>
        <p>No. We run the audit using publicly available tools, Google PageSpeed, Search Console public data, manual review, and SEO analysis tools. No passwords, no login access required.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What if my website is new?</summary>
        <p>New websites benefit most from audits, it's the ideal time to catch structural SEO issues before Google has already indexed the wrong signals. We'll identify what to set up correctly from the start.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Will you try to sell me something after sending the audit?</summary>
        <p>We'll send the report without any sales pressure. If you have questions about specific issues or want to know what fixing them would cost, you can ask us, but we won't follow up with sales calls if you don't want them.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I get an audit if I'm not in Ahmedabad?</summary>
        <p>Yes. We audit websites from anywhere in India and internationally. Location doesn't affect the quality or scope of the website audit.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<CtaBanner
  title="Ready to Find Out What's Holding Your Website Back?"
  subtitle="Submit your website URL above and receive your free 25-point audit report within 48 hours."
